   326                              <1>                                         ; set if you want an interrupt to fire
   327                              <1>                                         ; whenever the completion of the last
   328                              <1>                                         ; valid buffer.
   329                              <1> RR                      equ     BIT1    ; reset registers.  Nukes all regs
